=== Purpose of This Document

The curriculum includes directed imaginal and inner work practices — principally the Desoille Directed Waking Dream sequences — involving deliberate contact with unconscious material. These practices carry inherent psychological risk for some individuals. This document discloses those risks specifically, identifies the student populations for whom the practices are contraindicated, and defines the boundaries of Academy and Guide conduct.

